OL,3,CNew offence recommended in wake of
OL,4,CSouthport attack
OL,6,FThe Government says a new offence of
OL,7,Fplanning mass killings should be
OL,8,Fbrought in, as ITV News' UK Editor
OL,9,FPaul Brand explains
OL,11,FThe UK's terror watchdog has
OL,12,Frecommended a new offence to prevent
OL,13,Fmass casualty attacks before they
OL,14,Fhappen should be considered in light
OL,15,Fof the Southport murders.
OL,17,FBut the review commissioned by the
OL,18,FHome Secretary following the attacks
OL,19,Fin July, also concluded that the
OL,20,Fterrorism definition should not be
OL,21,Fchanged.
