OL,6,FJonathan Hall KC said the legal
OL,7,Fdefinition is "already wide" and
OL,8,Fexpanding the threshold would
OL,9,F"increase the possibility of
OL,10,Finaccurate use and, in theory, abuse".
OL,12,FMr Hall also warned that
OL,13,Fdisinformation in the aftermath of the
OL,14,FSouthport killings and allegations of
OL,15,Fa "cover-up" risked far more prejudice
OL,16,Fto any trial than undisputed facts
OL,17,Fabout the attacker.
