OL,6,F"In the digital era, if the police do
OL,7,Fnot take the lead in providing clear,
OL,8,Faccurate and sober details about an
OL,9,Fattack like Southport, others will,"
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,F"Social media is a source of news for
OL,13,Fmany people and near silence in the
OL,14,Fface of horrific events of major
OL,15,Fpublic interest is no longer an option.
OL,17,F"Whether or not the Contempt of Court
OL,18,FAct 1981 needs reform, the nature of
OL,19,Fprejudice in the digital age needs to
OL,20,Fbe understood."
