OL,7,FJanuary to examine terror legislation
OL,8,F"in light of modern threats we face",
OL,9,Falso warns that extending terror
OL,10,Fliability could result in
OL,11,F"unacceptable restrictions on freedom
OL,12,Fof expression".
OL,14,FHe warned: "The risk of unintended
OL,15,Fconsequences through rushed reform is
OL,16,Fextremely high.
