OL,6,FAxel Rudakubana was jailed for a
OL,7,Fminimum of 52 years for the murders of
OL,8,Fthree girls and attempted murders of
OL,9,Feight other children, who cannot be
OL,10,Fnamed for legal reasons, class
OL,11,Finstructor Leanne Lucas and
OL,12,Fbusinessman John Hayes at a Taylor
OL,13,FSwift-themed dance class in July 2024.
OL,15,FDespite contact with state agencies
OL,16,Fsuch as Prevent, aimed at countering
OL,17,Fterrorism, authorities failed to stop
OL,18,Fthe attack which claimed the lives of
OL,19,FAlice da Silva Aguiar, nine, Bebe
OL,20,FKing, six, and Elsie Dot Stancombe,
OL,21,Fseven.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/16
