OL,6,FRudakubana's acts of extreme violence
OL,7,Fwere not considered terrorism under
OL,8,Fexisting laws because there was no
OL,9,Fevidence of his purpose being to
OL,10,Fadvance an ideological cause as set
OL,11,Fout in the terror definition.
OL,13,FBut Mr Hall said: "Such is the
OL,14,Ffunctional importance of the terrorism
OL,15,Fdefinition, that redefinition would
OL,16,Falter the landscape.
OL,26,@uD@SOU
