OL,6,F"It would risk major false positives `
OL,7,Fthe prosecution of people who by no
OL,8,Fstretch of the imagination are
OL,9,Fterrorists ` and extend terrorism
OL,10,Fliability into novel terrain.
OL,12,F"People swapping violent war footage
OL,13,Fwould be at risk of encouraging
OL,14,Fterrorism, resulting in unacceptable
OL,15,Frestrictions on freedom of expression."
OL,17,FHe added that the current "very wide"
OL,18,Fdefinition depends on the discretion
OL,19,Fof the police and authorities on
OL,20,Fdeciding who to arrest and prosecute.
