OL,6,F"It has been my experience that this
OL,7,Fdiscretion has been exercised capably
OL,8,Fand well, so that individuals are not
OL,9,Fexposed to irrationality, heavy-
OL,10,Fhandedness or bias.
OL,12,F"But this is a product of a mature and
OL,13,Fdefined system operating with a
OL,14,Ffamiliar threshold.
OL,16,FAltering the threshold would not only
OL,17,Fexpand the reach of terrorism
OL,18,Flegislation but would increase the
OL,19,Fpossibility of inaccurate use and, in
