OL,6,FHe said for some cases it will be
OL,7,Fclear to investigators the attack was
OL,8,Ffor "purely personal motives" and
OL,9,Fsaying it is not treated as terrorism
OL,10,Fmakes "good sense to do so".
OL,12,FHe referenced the case of Nicholas
OL,13,FProsper, 19, who murdered his mother
OL,14,Fand two siblings and was on his was to
OL,15,Fcarry out a mass shooting at his old
OL,16,Fprimary school when he was stopped by
OL,17,Fpolice.
