OL,6,FA loaded shotgun was found hidden in
OL,7,Fbushes nearby, with a bag of more than
OL,8,F30 cartridges, when officers spotted
OL,9,Fhim in Bramingham Road, Luton.
OL,11,FThere is not a specific offence that
OL,12,Fhe could be charged with for planning
OL,13,Fthe school shooting because his plot
OL,14,Fwould not be defined as terrorism.
OL,16,F"The key point to make is that
OL,17,Fterrorism legislation is not the UK's
OL,18,Fmain protection against this sort of
OL,19,Fattacker: what counts is gun control,"
OL,20,Fhe said.
