OL,7,Fcopycats that it is "foreseeable" that
OL,8,Fother types of violent attacks will
OL,9,Fstart a copycat craze, "most likely
OL,10,Famongst the cohort of isolated often
OL,11,Fbullied teenagers with poor mental
OL,12,Fhealth, neurodivergence or personality
OL,13,Fdisorder for whom grudges and
