OL,6,FInstead, the watchdog recommended
OL,7,Fcreating an offence to prevent mass
OL,8,Fcasualty attacks before they happen,
OL,9,Fsimilar to terrorism offences applying
OL,10,Fto an offender preparing for an attack.
OL,12,F"It has become clear to me during the
OL,13,Fpreparation of this report during
OL,14,FJanuary and February 2025 that there
OL,15,Fis a real and not theoretical gap for
OL,16,Flone individuals who plan mass
OL,17,Fkillings," he said.
