OL,6,FHe said: "He's recommending that we
OL,7,Fdon't widen the definition of
OL,8,Fterrorism and to be honest I think
OL,9,Fhe's got this wrong.
OL,11,F"I think that anybody watching this
OL,12,Ffrom home can see that what happened
OL,13,Fin Southport last July was terrorism.
OL,15,F"We need to be brave and confident
OL,16,Fenough in calling it terrorism when
OL,17,Fthat's what it is. Although I respect
OL,18,Fhis independence, he's called this one
OL,19,Fwrong."
